---
title: Asian Soy & Lime Chicken with Garlic Rice & Mint
description: Thai cuisine is genius about using aromatics to add flavour. Here, we’ve doubled up on superstar ingredients, with fragrant
makrut lime leaves in the glaze for the chicken and a garnish of mint so it smells and tastes like the tropical holiday you deserve.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-makrut-lime-chicken-afb364b6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/asian-soy-lime-chicken-604ff367dd5751261d4dc50a-2d39d83b.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/asian-soy-and-lime-chicken-604ff367dd5751261d4dc50a
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: Asian
